                                | Don&apos;t have an account? 
                                a.link-info.text-decoration-none(href='#!') Register here
                .col-sm-6.px-0.d-none.d-sm-block
                    img.w-100.vh-100(src='/images/saman-taheri-MXMs8q2OjeA-unsplash.jpg' alt='Login image' style='object-fit: cover; object-position: left;')
